data.description: Hey you. Come on home. Ready to move in basement rancher with a ginormous screened in back porch. Like-new HVAC, hot water heater, stove and dishwasher. Updated kitchen with newer cabinets and granite countertops. Living room with plenty of natural light. 3-car garage and plenty of storage in the basement. New gutters. Your house will be the new entertainment spot for your friends and family with the bar area in the basement and the screened in back porch. Fenced in front yard for the dogs. Half acre lot. Come on home!
